      "header_utils_desc": "Essential utilities pamoja na project management, msaada rasilimali, na user hali geuza. Geuza kati mwalimu na mwanafunzi hali au fikia imehifadhiwa kazi.",
      "header_tools_title": "haraka zana",
      "header_tools_desc": "Power zana kwa maudhui creation na AI assistance. Fikia kuandika workshop, mazungumzo assistant, na nyingine productivity vipengele.",
      "lesson_plan_title": "somo Planning",
