      "sidebar_glossary_title": "Smart kamusi",
      "sidebar_glossary_desc": "kiotomatiki extracted msamiati istilahi na fasili, tafsiri, na kuona aikoni. Hariri istilahi, ongeza tafsiri, na unda kadi za kumbukumbu.",
      "sidebar_simplified_title": "Simplified toleo",
