    "concept_sort_game": "inafanya kazi dhana panga mchezo kiolesura kwa categorization fanya mazoezi. Buruta kipengele ndani sahihi jamii buckets kwa demonstrate understanding ya darasaification dhana. Immediate maoni inaonyesha sahihi na incorrect placements. msaada 2-4 jamii na yoyote nambari ya sortable kipengele. Kubwa kwa msamiati tiers, science darasaifications, au grammar sorting.",
