      "unknown_error": "unknown hitilafu",
      "idle": "Bofya \"Endesha audit\" kwa scan sasa tazama kwa WCAG 2.1 na AA violations. ya kwanza endesha takes ~2 sekunde kwa pakia axe-core (~350 KB minified) kutoka CDN; subsequent runs ni instant.",
