      "no_violations": "✅ No WCAG 2.1 /AA violations found katika sasa tazama by axe-core. (Note: automated audits catch ~30-50% ya real ufikivu issues. Combine na kibodi tour, skrini-reader preview, na mwongozo kagua.)",
      "rule_singular": "rule",
